&lt;strong&gt;OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;

Are there angels and demons all around us? Does God speak through people speaking gibberish? Are there really places like heaven and hell after we die? There are some strange things in Scripture and it&rsquo;s not very often that we get to address these topics, so we set aside an entire series to talk about the things that make us raise our eyebrows a little bit.

The Unexplainable is a series that helps us explore some of the stranger things we witness in Scripture. People believe many different things regarding these subjects, so let&rsquo;s sit down and work through the key passages of Scripture to seek a better understanding of ourselves, our world, and our God.

&lt;strong&gt;OUTLINE&lt;/strong&gt;

&lt;strong&gt;Angels and Demons&lt;/strong&gt; // Luke 24:36-43, 4:31-35, Rev. 12:9

&lt;strong&gt;Spiritual Warfare&lt;/strong&gt; // Ephesians 6:10-20

