The greatest polling game that has ever been created. Alright, I can't make that promise, but this game is really fun for groups of 10 and all the way to groups of 1,000. One person from the group has to guess what percentage of people fit into the question on the screen. The audience then responds by either sitting (lower than the number given) or standing (higher than the number given). Check out what a typical game of Pollsters looks like:
&lt;ul&gt;
 	&lt;li&gt;Have a volunteer come up from the crowd.&lt;/li&gt;
 	&lt;li&gt;You can&rsquo;t look up the answer on your phone.&lt;/li&gt;
