Description:
'Malice in Wonderland' is a 3-week series about the fall of man, and the redemption that follows.

'Week 1 - The Original Wonderland' is focused on the perfect world Adam and Eve had in Genesis 2, and why that's important.
'Week 2 - Wonderland Lost' is all about the fall of man in Genesis 3, and the implication it has for us as a human race.
'Week 3 - Wonderland 2.0' is all about the work that Jesus did on the Cross to reverse the curse of sin and death and allow us to enter into Wonderland 2.0 - heaven!

The manuscript for each week is around 2,500 words.

I pray that this series will be a blessing to you and your group. Have fun with it!

