Introduction and overview of the Book of Exodus
&lt;em&gt;The next ten weeks of devotionals will hopefully give you a place to read, process, and journal through the Book of Exodus. We want to emphasize the quality of your reading of the Bible and not the quantity. The Exodus Bible Devotional has very limited original content, instead we are intending you to use the Bible Devotional as a guide for you to work through as you explore Scripture. The content will all be questions that help you discover the meaning of each verse of the Book of Exodus. We hope that you write down your answers and reflections in a journal or print these pages out and write beside each question.&lt;/em&gt;

&lt;strong&gt;How do you use this product?&lt;/strong&gt;
Print one of these for each of your students, post them as blog entries, or text them out to a group. Encourage your students to be in God's Word by reading it together and embracing accountability.

